data.description: CB471  COUNTRY LIVING WITH A VIEW!    8.48 acre parcel, fenced and cross fenced for livestock, YEAR ROUND POND, water troughs and dog kennels.   Rolling terrain, minutes from town yet truly in the country.  Adjacent to an 80 acre parcel of rolling hills, outstanding sunsets from the back patio of this spacious 3/2 home.  All large rooms and a fabulous wood burning stove, plus central heat, central air and evaporative cooling.    Dual pane windows, NEW carpet and interior paint, tile floors and counters.   Oversized 2 car garage with an storage room, large laundry room with a full wall pantry. Detached carport and workshop too.
